I wish my baby kitty would snuggle like this....

She never has before - she was sitting on my chest purring while I was on my back, but I wanted to go to sleep on my side - guess she hadn't had enough face-time cos she just curled right up in there. <3
... that would be an unusual decision for me, I think. I did not get my forehead tattooed :)
